Subject: Endpoint Protector license usage
Description:
I have some more questions.

I am looking via Licensing Status and can see we have 1356 Online:
 

But when I go to either, View Licences or Device Control > Computers, I can only see 200, even when I have selected to see All. There are not multiple pages to search through.

There are no filters that I am aware of that is limiting this further, are you aware of any issue in 5.9.4.0 or a fix for this?
Solution_Comment__c: The view is limited by a "Device Control > Global Settings" setting called Display settings.
